{"tid":664793,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] [瘋味]又一力作","createTime":"2018-05-14T11:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T07:50:36.000Z","uid":5834,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"44dc41dd38d7b5c703ea589d11b2aba58e23407a","tid":664793,"uid":5834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒在微博上傳視頻，並配文稱：&ldquo;聽新歌混音，別煩我&rdquo;視頻中，只見謝霆鋒趴在廚房的案台上，他一左一右各放一個喇叭，伴隨著悠揚的歌聲，他緩緩地回頭看了鏡頭一眼，然後默默地繼續趴在案台上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://f.sinaimg.cn/ent/transform/671/w389h282/20180514/PfUG-hapkuvk4458761.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ff.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Ftransform%2F671%2Fw389h282%2F20180514%2FPfUG-hapkuvk4458761.gif&h=2006ac36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友紛紛表示：&ldquo;哥，聽歌就聽歌，你把頭埋進兩個音響中間這是什麼酷刑&rdquo;&ldquo;好，不煩你&rdquo;&ldquo;嘻嘻嘻，脾氣還不小。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dc445a5a5535fd52e0856f105aa4c4f8d7ee75","tid":664793,"uid":5834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"瘋瘋型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7910e4b97c18d43949804e8712ec0aa62a751f7b","tid":664793,"uid":5077,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T11:27:27.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔係明星，佢一早俾人捉咗入青山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686e0ed2a350a3e5ab97b9b615124b245fc7d66a","tid":664793,"uid":31408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T11:27:34.000Z","msg":"條友真係愈嚟愈黐線"},{"pid":"883048fb715da27388ae73f6a7d23a9429